            <category term="Call of Duty Modern Warfare 2 Tips &amp; Tricks"/>

        <updated>2022-12-22T19:11:18-05:00</updated>
            <summary>
                <![CDATA[
                        <img src="https://consoleloop.com/media/posts/135/thumbnail.webp" alt="Call of Duty Modern Warfare II Safe Locations Tips and Tricks" />
                    To obtain the Gentleman Thief achievement you will need to find all 3 safe locations which I will guide you through below. For A Video&hellip;
                ]]>
            </summary>
        <content type="html">
            <![CDATA[
                    <p><img src="https://consoleloop.com/media/posts/135/thumbnail.webp" class="type:primaryImage" alt="Call of Duty Modern Warfare II Safe Locations Tips and Tricks" /></p>
                <p>To obtain the Gentleman Thief achievement you will need to find all 3 safe locations which I will guide you through below.</p>
<div class="gallery-wrapper"><div class="gallery"  data-is-empty="false" data-translation="Add images" data-columns="1">
<figure class="gallery__item"><a href="https://consoleloop.com/media/posts/135/gallery/Safe1-1.png" data-size="1920x1080"><img loading="lazy" src="https://consoleloop.com/media/posts/135/gallery/Safe1-1-thumbnail.png" alt="" width="720" height="405"></a>
<figcaption>First Safe - Step 1 - Found In El Sin Nombre, Play Until You Come Across This Hallway</figcaption>
</figure>
<figure class="gallery__item"><a href="https://consoleloop.com/media/posts/135/gallery/Safe1-2.png" data-size="1920x1080"><img loading="lazy" src="https://consoleloop.com/media/posts/135/gallery/Safe1-2-thumbnail.png" alt="" width="720" height="405"></a>
<figcaption>First Safe - Step 2 - Turn Left Through Doorway</figcaption>
</figure>
<figure class="gallery__item"><a href="https://consoleloop.com/media/posts/135/gallery/Safe1-3.png" data-size="1920x1080"><img loading="lazy" src="https://consoleloop.com/media/posts/135/gallery/Safe1-3-thumbnail.png" alt="" width="720" height="405"></a>
<figcaption>First Safe - Step 3 - Go Up Stairs With Security Guard</figcaption>
</figure>
<figure class="gallery__item"><a href="https://consoleloop.com/media/posts/135/gallery/Safe1-4.png" data-size="1920x1080"><img loading="lazy" src="https://consoleloop.com/media/posts/135/gallery/Safe1-4-thumbnail.png" alt="" width="720" height="405"></a>
<figcaption>First Safe - Step 4 - Go Through Pool Room</figcaption>
</figure>
<figure class="gallery__item"><a href="https://consoleloop.com/media/posts/135/gallery/Safe1-5.png" data-size="1920x1080"><img loading="lazy" src="https://consoleloop.com/media/posts/135/gallery/Safe1-5-thumbnail.png" alt="" width="720" height="405"></a>
<figcaption>First Safe - Step 5 - Do A Takedown On Guard</figcaption>
</figure>
<figure class="gallery__item"><a href="https://consoleloop.com/media/posts/135/gallery/Safe1-6.png" data-size="1920x1080"><img loading="lazy" src="https://consoleloop.com/media/posts/135/gallery/Safe1-6-thumbnail.png" alt="" width="720" height="405"></a>
<figcaption>First Safe - Step 6 - Follow Hallway</figcaption>
</figure>
<figure class="gallery__item"><a href="https://consoleloop.com/media/posts/135/gallery/Safe1-7.png" data-size="1920x1080"><img loading="lazy" src="https://consoleloop.com/media/posts/135/gallery/Safe1-7-thumbnail.png" alt="" width="720" height="405"></a>
<figcaption>First Safe - Step 7 - Enter Door On Left</figcaption>
</figure>
<figure class="gallery__item"><a href="https://consoleloop.com/media/posts/135/gallery/Safe1-8.png" data-size="1920x1080"><img loading="lazy" src="https://consoleloop.com/media/posts/135/gallery/Safe1-8-thumbnail.png" alt="" width="720" height="405"></a>
<figcaption>First Safe - Step 8 - Take A Right To Find The Hidden Safe</figcaption>
</figure>
<figure class="gallery__item"><a href="https://consoleloop.com/media/posts/135/gallery/Safe1-9.png" data-size="1920x1080"><img loading="lazy" src="https://consoleloop.com/media/posts/135/gallery/Safe1-9-thumbnail.png" alt="" width="720" height="405"></a>
<figcaption>First Safe - Step 9 - Enter: 02 - 02 - 19</figcaption>
</figure>
<figure class="gallery__item"><a href="https://consoleloop.com/media/posts/135/gallery/Safe2-1.png" data-size="1920x1080"><img loading="lazy" src="https://consoleloop.com/media/posts/135/gallery/Safe2-1-thumbnail.png" alt="" width="720" height="405"></a>
<figcaption>Second Safe - Step 1 - Found In Alone, Play Until You Find This Lit Up Room</figcaption>
</figure>
<figure class="gallery__item"><a href="https://consoleloop.com/media/posts/135/gallery/Safe2-2.png" data-size="1920x1080"><img loading="lazy" src="https://consoleloop.com/media/posts/135/gallery/Safe2-2-thumbnail.png" alt="" width="720" height="405"></a>
<figcaption>Second Safe - Step 2 - Turn Left To Find The Safe Hidden Behind A Locked Door</figcaption>
</figure>
<figure class="gallery__item"><a href="https://consoleloop.com/media/posts/135/gallery/Safe2-3.png" data-size="1920x1080"><img loading="lazy" src="https://consoleloop.com/media/posts/135/gallery/Safe2-3-thumbnail.png" alt="" width="720" height="405"></a>
<figcaption>Second Safe - Step 3 - Enter: 10 - 10 - 80</figcaption>
</figure>
<figure class="gallery__item"><a href="https://consoleloop.com/media/posts/135/gallery/Safe3-1.png" data-size="1920x1080"><img loading="lazy" src="https://consoleloop.com/media/posts/135/gallery/Safe3-1-thumbnail.png" alt="" width="720" height="405"></a>
<figcaption>Third Safe - Step 1 - Continue From The Previous Safe Until You Find A Stealth Mission</figcaption>
</figure>
<figure class="gallery__item"><a href="https://consoleloop.com/media/posts/135/gallery/Safe3-2.png" data-size="1920x1080"><img loading="lazy" src="https://consoleloop.com/media/posts/135/gallery/Safe3-2-thumbnail.png" alt="" width="720" height="405"></a>
<figcaption>Third Safe - Step 2 - Work Your Way Left</figcaption>
</figure>
<figure class="gallery__item"><a href="https://consoleloop.com/media/posts/135/gallery/Safe3-3.png" data-size="1920x1080"><img loading="lazy" src="https://consoleloop.com/media/posts/135/gallery/Safe3-3-thumbnail.png" alt="" width="720" height="405"></a>
<figcaption>Third Safe - Step 3 - Take Out Guard And Turn Right</figcaption>
</figure>
<figure class="gallery__item"><a href="https://consoleloop.com/media/posts/135/gallery/Safe3-4.png" data-size="1920x1080"><img loading="lazy" src="https://consoleloop.com/media/posts/135/gallery/Safe3-4-thumbnail.png" alt="" width="720" height="405"></a>
<figcaption>Third Safe - Step 4 - Doors At The End But Be Prepared For A Fight</figcaption>
</figure>
<figure class="gallery__item"><a href="https://consoleloop.com/media/posts/135/gallery/Safe3-5.png" data-size="1920x1080"><img loading="lazy" src="https://consoleloop.com/media/posts/135/gallery/Safe3-5-thumbnail.png" alt="" width="720" height="405"></a>
<figcaption>Third Safe - Step 5 - Enter: 37 - 60 - 80</figcaption>
</figure>
</div></div>
